====Noun====
{{en-noun|es}}

#[[Beeswax]].
#[[Earwax]].
#Any oily, water-resistant substance; normally long-chain [[hydrocarbon]]s, [[alcohol]]s or [[ester]]s
#Any [[preparation]] containing wax, used as a [[polish]]
#A [[phonograph]] [[record]]

